graph TD
    subgraph Client
        MobileApp[Flutter / React Native Customer App]
        WebDashboard[Control Center Dashboard]
    end

    subgraph Cloud Backend
        FastAPI[FastAPI Telemetry Gateway]
        DB[(SQLite / PostgreSQL database)]
        WebSockets[WebSocket Telemetry Hub]
    end

    subgraph Drone System
        Companion[Raspberry Pi 5 / NVIDIA Jetson]
        YOLO[YOLOv11 Edge AI]
        FC[PX4 Flight Autopilot]
        MAVLink[MAVLink Serial Link]
    end

    MobileApp -->|POST /orders| FastAPI
    WebDashboard -->|GET /fleet/health| FastAPI
    FastAPI <-->|Read / Write| DB
    WebSockets -->|Live Telemetry Broadcast| WebDashboard
    FastAPI <-->|WebSocket Status Streams| WebSockets

    Companion <-->|MAVLink Protocol| FC
    FC -->|Sensor Data| Companion
    Companion -->|Camera Frames| YOLO
    YOLO -->|Avoidance Vectors| FC
    Companion -->|POST /telemetry/report| FastAPI
